OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FSarina Wiegman admitted England were
OL,8,Fnot at their best after a 4-0 drubbing
OL,9,Fin Spain dented their direct
OL,10,Fqualification hopes for the Women's
OL,11,FWorld Cup.
OL,13,FThe Lionesses had entered the match
OL,14,Fleading qualifying group Group A3 with
OL,15,Ffour wins, but were handed an early
OL,16,Fblow when Patri Guijarro put the hosts
OL,17,Fahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FPutellas then struck twice either side
OL,8,Fof the break and Claudia Pina
OL,9,Fcompleted a ruthless Spanish display,
OL,10,Fmoving them to the top of the group
OL,11,Fand level with England on 12 points
OL,12,Fafter five matches.
OL,14,FDefeat for Sarina Wiegman's side means
OL,15,Fthe battle for direct qualification
OL,16,Finto next year's tournament in Brazil
OL,17,Fnow boils down to Tuesday's games,
OL,18,Fwhere the Lionesses host Ukraine at
OL,19,Fthe Hill Dickinson Stadium and Spain
OL,20,Fface Iceland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FWith captain Leah Williamson ruled out
OL,8,Fthrough injury, Keira Walsh skippered
OL,9,FEngland and had a cross comfortably
OL,10,Fcollected by Cata Coll at her near
OL,11,Fpost in the opening stages.
OL,13,FHowever, Spain enjoyed the early share
OL,14,Fof possession and Lucia Corrales sent
OL,15,Fa menacing cross in for Putellas, but
OL,16,Fher header bounced past the post.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FPutellas hit a curling delivery into
OL,8,FEdna Imade which Hannah Hampton was
OL,9,Fable to save before England had an
OL,10,Fopportunity, with Walsh blasting an
OL,11,Feffort from outside of the area
OL,12,Fnarrowly over the crossbar.
OL,14,FSpain continued to control
OL,15,Fproceedings, taking the lead 19
OL,16,Fminutes in when Guijarro weaved into
OL,17,Fthe middle of the pitch from the left
OL,18,Fflank and from around 25 yards out,
OL,19,Fthe Barcelona midfielder slotted the
OL,20,Fball into the bottom corner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FHampton held Imade's header as the
OL,8,Fhosts looked to quickly strike and the
OL,9,FEngland goalkeeper was called into
OL,10,Faction again to comfortably hold
OL,11,FPutellas' effort after the Spanish
OL,12,Fmidfielder had been played into space
OL,13,Fon the edge of the box.
OL,15,FLauren James' cross flew across the
OL,16,Fface of goal, but Spain took charge
OL,17,Fagain as Vicky Lopez surged into the
OL,18,Farea and Lotte Wubben-Moy intervened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FThe hosts doubled their advantage in
OL,8,Fthe 37th minute when Mariona Caldentey
OL,9,Fthreaded the ball into Putellas, who
OL,10,Ffired home despite Hampton getting a
OL,11,Fhand to the shot.
OL,13,FEngland had an opportunity after the
OL,14,Fbreak when Georgia Stanway blasted a
OL,15,Fstrike past the post, but Spain soon
OL,16,Fextended their lead further in the
OL,17,F55th minute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
