FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FPutellas had an initial effort well
OL,8,Fstopped on the goal line by Lucy
OL,9,FBronze, but the ball bounced off the
OL,10,Fpost and the Spain forward reacted
OL,11,Fquickly to pounce and stab home her
OL,12,Fsecond of the night.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
