FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FThe home side continued to pile on the
OL,8,Fpressure as Hampton made a stunning
OL,9,Fsave to tip away Guijarro's header and
OL,10,FLopez blasted an effort into the side-
OL,11,Fnetting.
OL,13,FEngland searched for a response, with
OL,14,FAlex Greenwood's cross palmed away by
OL,15,FColl and the ball fell to Bronze, but
OL,16,Fher attempt was blocked.
OL,18,FSubstitute Aitana Bonmati made an
OL,19,Finstant impact from the bench to set
OL,20,Fup Pina, who fired the ball into the
OL,21,Fbottom corner in the 78th minute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,FBonmati nearly added to a ruthless
OL,8,FSpanish performance in the final
OL,9,Fminutes after she forced Hampton into
OL,10,Fa save at her near post.
OL,12,FReflecting on the game, Wiegman told
OL,13,FITV: "Indeed, a very difficult night.
OL,14,FI think the difference tonight between
OL,15,FSpain and England was big.
OL,26,@uD@FOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,F"We weren't at our best ` although I
OL,8,Fthought we started well ` but when
OL,9,Fthey got into a rhythm and they got
OL,10,Ftheir first goal, I think we just
OL,11,Fdidn't play to our strengths too much
OL,12,Fand they played really well.
OL,14,F"That showed the difference tonight.
OL,15,FThat indeed is very disappointing.
OL,17,F"It also has to do with a very good
OL,18,FSpain tonight, that's never an excuse
OL,19,Fthat you lose 4-0.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,F"We started well, we wanted to harm
OL,8,Fthem in the back and in the first half
OL,9,Fespecially after those first minutes
OL,10,Fthat we started well, we played short,
OL,11,Fwe played back all the time and that
OL,12,Fplayed to their strengths a little bit.
OL,14,F"We harmed ourselves because we lost
OL,15,Fthe ball a couple of times more where
OL,16,Fthey got chances but we should have
OL,17,Fskipped players, we wanted to get in
OL,18,Fthe pockets or in behind them.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780733118
OL,3,CEngland's automatic World Cup
OL,4,Cqualification hopes dented by Spain
OL,5,Cdefeat
OL,7,F"We just didn't get there and when we
OL,8,Fdid we found it really hard to keep
OL,9,Fthe ball. I think that has to do with
OL,10,Fus, it also has to do with the
OL,11,Fstrength of Spain at this moment."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
